---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Zephyr DJ Co."
	description="Modern wedding DJ + lighting for unforgettable celebrations"
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	headerNote="Modern wedding DJ + lighting"
>
	<section class="intro-section glow-card">
		<h2 class="headline">Elevate your night.</h2>
		<p class="tagline">Curated mixes, seamless hosting, and elegant lighting that turns moments into memories.</p>
		<div class="highlights">
			<div class="highlight glass-surface">
				<h3>Signature Sound</h3>
				<p>Custom playlists, live mixing, and pro-grade audio tuned to your space and crowd.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="highlight glass-surface">
				<h3>Atmospheric Lighting</h3>
				<p>Dynamic uplighting, tasteful effects, and room-wide ambiance that feels cinematic.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="highlight glass-surface">
				<h3>White‑Glove Service</h3>
				<p>Clear timelines, flawless cues, and vendor coordination so your night flows effortlessly.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="packages">
		<h3 class="section-title">Popular Packages</h3>
		<div class="package-grid">
			<div class="package-card glass-surface">
				<h4>Essentials</h4>
				<ul>
					<li>Ceremony + Reception coverage</li>
					<li>Pro audio + wireless mics</li>
					<li>Classic dancefloor lighting</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="package-card glass-surface featured">
				<h4>Signature</h4>
				<ul>
					<li>Full-day coverage</li>
					<li>Custom playlists + live mixing</li>
					<li>Room uplighting + spotlighting</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="package-card glass-surface">
				<h4>Grand</h4>
				<ul>
					<li>Extended coverage</li>
					<li>Enhanced lighting design</li>
					<li>Grand intros + special effects</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="why-us glow-card">
		<h3 class="section-title">Why Couples Choose Us</h3>
		<ul class="pill-list">
			<li>Intentional music curation</li>
			<li>Elegant, minimal footprint</li>
			<li>Clear MC presence without clichés</li>
			<li>On-time, on-cue, on-point</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<div class="cta">
		<a href="/bookings" class="cta-button button-neon">Check availability</a>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.headline {
		font-size: 2.4rem;
		margin: 0 0 .25rem 0;
		background: linear-gradient(92deg, #8a2be2, var(--accent));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		background-clip: text;
		color: transparent;
		text-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(35, 55, 255, 0.2);
	}
	.tagline { color: rgb(var(--gray)); margin: 0 0 1rem 0; }

	.intro-section { padding: 1.25rem; }
	.highlights { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
	.highlight { padding: 1rem; }
	.highlight h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem 0; }

	.packages { margin-top: 2rem; }
	.section-title { margin: 0 0 .75rem 0; letter-spacing: .04em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgb(var(--gray)); }
	.package-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
	.package-card { padding: 1rem; }
	.package-card ul { margin: .5rem 0 0 1.25rem; }
	.package-card.featured { box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.08), 0 0 40px rgba(35,55,255,0.18); }

	.why-us { padding: 1.25rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
	.pill-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .5rem; }
	.pill-list li { border: 1px solid rgba(var(--gray), .25); border-radius: 999px; padding: .4rem .7rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,.02); }

	.cta { text-align: center; margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0; }
	.cta-button { display: inline-block; padding: .8rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; color: white; background: var(--accent); }

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.highlights { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.package-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
	}
</style>
